    "body": "Hi @jasperkennis :) We provide connectors for such a case. In the [connectRange](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors/connectRange.html) you will be able to refine a range and build your own UI. We do not provide a widget with a single handle as we thought it was too much of an edge case at the time, but we're always listening to new feedback :)",
